{"Sid":0,"Did":126738,"Id":"602997","Title":"掃笏正勉堂","ImageUrl":"https://dcm.s3.hicloud.net.tw/excel/place/2020-11-11/f52184de-33a1-4d5a-8a72-52adcf89a439/collection/0714ca1c-678f-45bc-b834-2cfee8fd4b66/109-sea-pa-2367-202011062119345fa540d5733140.jpg","IndexCode":"Culture_Place","CustomColumns":{"Description":"\n\n　　「正勉堂」座落於五結鄉福興村，創立於1901年。因位於過去噶瑪蘭族掃笏社所在地，俗稱「掃笏廟」。\n\n　　「正勉堂」主祀王天君，當地人稱「恩師公」，是五聖恩主之一。據載最初為來自漳州漳浦藍姓家族所信奉的家神，因有替人扶鸞問事，十分靈驗，日漸興盛，成為掃笏地區的地方信仰中心。清代時期與羅東勸世堂、羅東勉民堂為蘭陽溪南三大鸞堂。\n\n　　每年農曆三月初八為正勉堂王天君開光紀念日，是掃笏地區的重要日子。堂廟於前一天晚上舉行祝壽典禮，當日也會舉行巡庄遶境活動。\n\n","Keyword_Rights_2":"CC BY","Keyword_Des_Rights_2":"CC0","Keyword_Longitude":"121.779804","Keyword_Latitude":"24.686464","Original_Url":"https://cmsdb.culture.tw/place/F45EAC01-2C43-4D58-8ACF-3F6CBE716000","Original_Identifier":"602997","Keyword_Subject_1":"民俗與宗教","alias":"","Keywords":"五結鄉 / 王天君 / 宜蘭鸞堂","historicalDates":"","LastUpdateTime":"2021/01/05 15:41:24","timelines":"","place":"","address":"宜蘭縣五結鄉興盛北路182巷16號","longitude":"121.779804","latitude":"24.686464","phone":"","Event":"","relationPeople":"","open":"0","free":"否","openTime":"","openTimeDescription":"","capacity":"","traffic":"","subjection":"","tag":"","situation":"","historicalDataBrief":"","historicalData":"","reference":"《台灣民間信仰神明大圖鑑》(進源出版社 陳進源 2012)","writer":"莊文生;鐘碧娟;謝淑娟","createOrgName":"宜蘭縣政府文化局","source":"","Keyword_Rights_1":"","AllImages":"https://dcm.s3.hicloud.net.tw/excel/place/2020-11-11/f52184de-33a1-4d5a-8a72-52adcf89a439/collectionOpen/13cf0fbb-dcee-4e6b-9586-1522b62e2bd7/109-sea-pa-2367-re-202011062121065fa540d5733140.jpg"}}